ther_(franchise)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Big_Brother_(franchise)\"}, {\"begin\": 3800, \"end\": 3806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.9649013626794584e-12, \"text\": \"Afrika\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maghreb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A dominant weekend for the SA teams in the URC has made a big impact on the latest log standings as the playoffs edge closer.\", \"from\": 3840, \"to\": 3965, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3867, \"end\": 3869, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.341898370805022e-25, \"text\": \"SA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 3883, \"end\": 3886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\", \"score\": 0.9985550265756621, \"rank\": 0.001440632113266695, \"text\": \"URC\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q10962\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Rugby_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheSouthAfrican.com is all about South Africa and the stories that affect South Africans, wherever they are in the world.\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 4090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4002, \"end\": 4014, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.5195269782140425e-19, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are independent.No agenda.No bias.\", \"from\": 4092, \"to\": 4129, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our offices are for administrative purposes only, no visitors will be accepted without an appointment.\", \"